text: Josef Zehnder (born 25 March 1944) is a Swiss ski jumper. He competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics, the 1968 Winter Olympics and the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
